    <p>Welcome to our website, and it is hoped you will be able to discover plenty of interesting details about our parish and its rich history.</p>
    <p>As we are small in number, the use of multiple social media platforms was thought impracticable for us to manage, and only ever had Facebook. However, we were able to launch Instagram in 2023, only possible with the assistance of Students of MTU. The full story may be found under the ‘Projects’ menu item.</p>
